reviews.review_text:
Better than the board I am hard pressed to give any audience capture 5 stars.  One, because the moniker of 5 stars is gratuitously abused, and secondly tapers can not control the their surroundings.  One careless crowd member can ruin a beautiful recording.

This recording has everything, depth, clarity, realism.  I rate it a 4.99998

Also, the tracking is incorrect.  Set II should read, T11 Playin' -> Playin' reprise Jam -> t12 China Doll -> Drums

The song list doesn't match up to the songs It's good recording but the song list doesn't match up to the songs. The encore, It's all over now baby blue, plays in the 1st set under the title Terrapin Station. The Wheel is actually Space. At first I thought the song titles were off by one song but then the encore came out of the blue in the 1st set. No pun intended. While the music quality is better than most, the labeling gets an F.
